#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "56_Feather"
msgid "This ain't over, Kiryu."
msgstr "Esto no ha acabado, Kiryu."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "68_Kiryu"
msgid "Snap out of your damn fantasy world, will you?"
msgstr "Sal de tu maldito mundo de fantasía, ¿quieres?"

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "80_Feather"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr "Uh, ¿y eso?"

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "92_Kiryu"
msgid "You think by beating me you'll get some kind of super power?"
msgstr "¿Crees que derrotarme te otorgara alguna especie de super poder?"

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "104_Feather"
msgid "Uh... Yeah."
msgstr "Eh... Sí."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "116_Kiryu"
msgid "Listen, even if you could beat me, there's no real point. At best, people might think you're a pretty good fighter."
msgstr "Escucha, incluso si pudieras derrotarme, no tiene sentido. Como mucho, la gente podría pensar que eres un luchador bastante bueno."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "128_Feather"
msgid "That ain't－"
msgstr "Eso no es-"

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "140_Kiryu"
msgid "Just hear me out."
msgstr "Solo presta atención."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "152_Kiryu"
msgid "Do you think that kind of power alone means a thing to the rest of the world? Sure, there are tons of yakuza who think as you do."
msgstr "¿Piensas que ese tipo de poder por sí solo significa algo para el resto del mundo? Claro, hay muchísimos yakuza que piensan como tú."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "164_Kiryu"
msgid "But for someone like you, who has the charisma to bring so many people together, is that really what you want to dedicate your life to?"
msgstr "Pero para alguien como tú, que tiene el carisma para unir a tanta gente, ¿es realmente a lo que quieres dedicar tu vida?"

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "176_Feather"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "188_Kiryu"
msgid "That reliance on power alone－it's no different from the way yakuza think."
msgstr "Esa dependencia en solo el poder - no es diferente de lo que piensa un yakuza."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "200_Kiryu"
msgid "Let's say you manage to get that power. The only thing waiting for you after that is a power struggle with the yakuza and the mafia."
msgstr "Digamos que consigues obtener es poder. La única cosa que te espera después de eso es una lucha de poder con la yakuza y la mafia."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "212_Kiryu"
msgid "If it comes to that, a lot of your men are going to get hurt or left behind. Is that really what you want?"
msgstr "Si se trata de eso, muchos de tus hombres van a salir heridos o se van a quedar atrás. ¿Es eso realmente lo que quieres?"

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "224_Feather"
msgid "No... I don't want that."
msgstr "No... No quiero eso."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "236_Kiryu"
msgid "Then you need to gather the ones that believe in you and find a new purpose. If you can't do that, then get the hell out of Kamurocho."
msgstr "Entonces tiene que reunir a los que creen en tí y encontrar un nuevo propósito. Si no puedes hacer eso, entonces largate de Kamurocho."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "248_Feather"
msgid "...!"
msgstr "¡...!"

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "260_Kiryu"
msgid "Kamurocho isn't the entire world. You could make it anywhere if you decide that fighting here isn't the smart choice."
msgstr "Kamurocho no es el mundo entero. Podrías lograrlo en cualquier lugar si decides que luchar aquí no es la decisión correcta."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "272_Kiryu"
msgid "I know because I got away from this town to make a new life in Okinawa. As young as you are, you've got plenty of time to start over."
msgstr "Lo sé porque me alejé de esta ciudad para hacer una nueva vida en Okinawa. Con lo joven que eres, tienes muchísimo tiempo para empezar de nuevo."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "284_Feather"
msgid "Okay, I hear you. I'm going to disband the Phoenix. I'm not leaving Kamurocho, though."
msgstr "Vale, te escucho. Voy a disolver a Phoenix. Pero no voy a abandonar Kamurocho."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "296_Feather"
msgid "I'm gonna live the right way, here in town. I'll show you, Kiryu-san!"
msgstr "Voy a vivir de la manera correcta, aquí en la ciudad. ¡Te lo enseñaré, Kiryu-san!"

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "308_Kiryu"
msgid "Heh. Give it your best shot."
msgstr "Je. Da lo mejor de tí."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "320_Feather"
msgid "Well... Catch ya later!"
msgstr "Bueno... ¡Nos vemos!"

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "380_Akaishi"
msgid "Kiryu-san, I'm truly impressed! Not only did you defeat their boss, you seem to have helped him become a new man!"
msgstr "¡Kiryu-san, estoy realmente sorprendido! No solo has derrotado a su jefe, ¡parece que le has ayudado a convertirse en una persona nueva!"

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "392_Akaishi"
msgid "Most of the top Phoenix members showed up at a local barbershop earlier. Apparently they intend to shave their heads and become monks."
msgstr "La mayoría de los miembros más destacados de Phoenix se presentaron en una barbería local. Al parecer, planean raparse la cabeza y convertirse en monjes."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "404_Kiryu"
msgid "I see..."
msgstr "Ya veo..."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "416_Akaishi"
msgid "Anyway, without their leader we won't have too many problems from this gang anymore. He really brought the whole group together."
msgstr "De todas formas, sin su lider ya no tendremos muchos problemas de esta banda. Él realmente unió a todo el grupo."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "428_Akaishi"
msgid "I'm sure we don't have to worry about them starting fights after this. What a relief."
msgstr "Estoy seguro que no tenemos que preocuparnos de que anden empezando peleas después de esto. Qué alivio."

#. y4:line_status=translated
#. y4:translated_by=Keiner
msgctxt "440_Akaishi"
msgid "Oh, this is a token of my appreciation."
msgstr "Ah, esto es una muestra de mi gratitud."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "464_Akaishi"
msgid "We appreciate all your help."
msgstr "Estamos realmente agradecidos con tu ayuda."

